T1  - The Great Depression in Italy: Trade Restrictions and Real Wage Rigidities
AU  - Perri, Fabrizio
AU  - Quadrini, Vincenzo
JO  - Review of Economic Dynamics
VL  - 5
IS  - 1
SP  - 128
EP  - 151
